          登录成功后验证身份即可领取礼品卡，安全、简单、高效。
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a href="#verify" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors shadow-gift text-lg font-medium">
